    "en": {
      "title": "Exclusive fuel arrangement for health workers, reinstated",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Health says that the Exclusive Fuel Arrangement for health care workers will be reinstated from tomorrow (15).",
        "Accordingly, the Health Ministry said that 109 fuel stations have been notified to provide fuel for health workers subject to limitations.",
        "Accordingly, motor vehicles will be allowed 20 litres, three wheelers will be allowed 8 litres, while motor bikes will be allowed 6 litres.",
        "The exclusive program, which underlined that health workers will be provided fuel on Fridays, was suspended.",
        "Mahinda, Basil & Attygalle pledge not to leave country until tomorrow (15)"
      ],
